Subject: [patch] v4l: bttv IR input driver update
From: kraxel@suse.de
Patch-mainline: not yet

This patch enables IR support for one AverMedia card and
drops a obsolete function.

Signed-off-by: Gerd Knorr <kraxel@bytesex.org>
